ze:12pt; font-style:italic; font-weight:bold">:</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt"> Good afternoon and welcome to the European Parliament. Thank you for inviting us to have an exchange of views ahead of what will be a very important European parliamentary week. I have known about the capacity of the House of Lords to scrutinise issues deeply ever since I started as a civil servant in the National Assembly way back in 1981. I have always admired the way the House of Lords challenges EU policies, and I can see that that </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">goes on</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">. I also </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">know the kind of </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">reports that </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">you </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">are </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">able to produce</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt"> on </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">these kinds of </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">topics, and </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">how these exchanges, either by writing procedure or by meetings, are useful for you as a fallback in your reports and as a testimony.</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt"> So </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">I am well aware of the context in </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">which I will deal</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt"> with </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">this meeting. </span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:200%; margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Gil